title: 3 bedroom ranch
description: This is a 3 bedroom ranch with a  large family and dinning room. Cathedral ceilings, appliances, propane and pellet stove heat. Large yard, walk to water. No utilities, water and sewer included .This is on Prudence Island. The only way on and off is by taking the Bristol Ferry.  It runs morning and late afternoon. It is a 25 minute ferry ride from Bristol R.I. Rent is $995.00 per month ( first and security required)
